\b  
\m
\v 4 \w Now|strong="H3117"\w* \w what|strong="H3372"\w* \w do|strong="H3068"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w against|strong="H6440"\w* \w Me|strong="H6440"\w*, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* Tyre, Sidon, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w all|strong="H1419"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* regions \w of|strong="H3068"\w* Philistia? \w Are|strong="H3117"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* rendering \w against|strong="H6440"\w* \w Me|strong="H6440"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* recompense? If \w you|strong="H6440"\w* retaliate \w against|strong="H6440"\w* \w Me|strong="H6440"\w*, \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* swiftly \w and|strong="H3068"\w* speedily return \w your|strong="H3068"\w* recompense \w upon|strong="H6440"\w* \w your|strong="H3068"\w* heads.  
\v 5 \w For|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w took|strong="H1961"\w* \w My|strong="H3605"\w* silver \w and|strong="H3068"\w* gold \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w carried|strong="H3068"\w* off \w My|strong="H3605"\w* finest treasures \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w your|strong="H3068"\w* temples.\f + \fr 3:5 \ft Or palaces\f*  
\v 6 You sold the people of Judah and Jerusalem to the Greeks,\f + \fr 3:6 \ft Or to the peoples of Javan\f* to send them far from their homeland.   
\b  
\m
\v 7 Behold, I will rouse them from the places to which you sold them; I will return your recompense upon your heads.  
\v 8 I will sell your sons and daughters into the hands of the people of Judah, and they will sell them to the Sabeans—to \w a|strong="H3068"\w* distant nation.”  
\b  
\m Indeed, the \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w* has spoken.   
\b  
\m
\v 9 Proclaim this among the nations:  
\b  
\q1 “Prepare for war;  
\q2 rouse the mighty men;  
\q1 let all the men of war  
\q2 advance and attack!   
\q1
\v 10 Beat your plowshares into swords  
\q2 and your pruning hooks into spears.  
\q2 Let the weak say, ‘I am strong!’   
\q1
\v 11 Come quickly, all you surrounding nations,  
\q2 and gather yourselves.  
\q1 Bring down Your mighty ones,  
\q2 \w O|strong="H3068"\w* \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w*.   
\b  
\q1
\v 12 Let the nations be roused  
