\q1
\v 13 Swing the sickle,  
\q2 for the harvest is ripe.\f + \fr 3:13 \ft LXX the harvest has come; see also Mark 4:29.\f*  
\q1 Come, trample the grapes,  
\q2 for the winepress is full;  
\q1 the wine vats overflow  
\q2 because their wickedness is great.   
\b  
\q1
\v 14 Multitudes, multitudes  
\q2 in the valley of decision!  
